solution.p:
We solve the inequality for y.
            4x - 3y \amp\ge 12 \amp \amp \blert{\text{Subtract}~ 4x~ \text{from both sides.}}
                -3y\amp\ge -4x + 12 \amp \amp \blert{\text{Divide both sides by}~ -3.}
                y\amp\le \frac{4}{3}x-4

